sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant IdP
    participant Gateway
    participant Service
    participant Redis

    User->>IdP: Authenticate
    IdP-->>User: access_token + refresh_token
    User->>Gateway: API request with access_token
    Gateway->>Service: Forward bearer token
    Service->>Service: Verify signature + exp + aud
    Service->>Redis: Check revoked:jti (or refresh cache)
    Redis-->>Service: not revoked
    Service-->>Gateway: allow
    Gateway-->>User: 200 response
